—ظSarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/polars_qcut.mdظ@a82a7269678d69b08dfe16d5f75dd67b8f2f62d937143837635d1ab16f87f87c²title: polars qcut‘¨ExamplesظذDivide a column into three categories according to pre-defined quantile probabilities.
