Content:
Divide a column into three categories according to pre-defined quantile probabilities.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [-2, -1, 0, 1, 2] | polars into-df | polars qcut [0.25, 0.75] --labels ["a", "b", "c"]


```
